# Card-audit (mtg-948 Part B): Swords to Plowshares — exile + controller-gains-life.
#
# Closed issue mtg-547 closed Swords to Plowshares as WORKING. Its two aspects:
#   1. SP$ ChangeZone Battlefield->Exile exiles the target creature.
#   2. Chained DB$ GainLife: the EXILED CREATURE'S CONTROLLER gains life equal
#      to the creature's power (Defined$ TargetedController, captured via
#      last-known-information before the exile — CR 608.2h).
# The Swords CASTER gains nothing.
#
# Wave 1 could not back this with the heuristic AI (it would not reliably cast
# Swords at a chosen target). With a script, P0 casts it at P1's own 2/2 so we
# can assert P1 (the controller of the exiled creature) gains exactly 2 life,
# the creature lands in exile, and P0's life is unchanged.
#
# Scenario:
#   - P0: Swords to Plowshares in hand, 1 Plains on the battlefield.
#   - P1: a Grizzly Bears (2/2) it controls, life 20.
#   - Script: P0 casts Swords to Plowshares targeting the Grizzly Bears.
#   - Bears is exiled; its controller (P1) gains 2 (its power) -> P1 = 22.
#   - P0 (caster) gains nothing -> P0 = 20.

[metadata]
Name:Card Audit - Swords to Plowshares Exiles and Gains Life
Goal:Win
Turns:1
Difficulty:Easy
Description:P0 scripts Swords to Plowshares onto P1's 2/2 Grizzly Bears. The creature is exiled and ITS controller (P1) gains 2 life (= its power); the caster gains nothing. Backs both aspects of issue mtg-547 (ChangeZone exile + TargetedController GainLife, CR 608.2h).

[state]
turn=1
activeplayer=p0
activephase=MAIN1
p0life=20
p0hand=Swords to Plowshares
p0battlefield=Plains
p0library=Forest;Forest;Forest;Forest;Forest

p1life=20
p1battlefield=Grizzly Bears
p1library=Mountain;Mountain;Mountain;Mountain;Mountain

[p0_script]
# Exile P1's own Grizzly Bears. Its controller (P1) gains life equal to its
# power (2). The `targeting` clause names the creature semantically.
cast Swords to Plowshares targeting Grizzly Bears

[assertions]
# Swords was actually cast.
spell cast Swords to Plowshares
# The exiled creature's CONTROLLER (P1) gained 2 life: 20 -> 22.
opponent life eq 22
# The caster (P0) gained nothing.
life eq 20
# The Grizzly Bears is in P1's exile zone (it left the battlefield to exile).
# This is durable: once exiled it never returns, so it holds at game end even
# though the heuristic plays lands onto P1's battlefield afterward.
opponent exile contains Grizzly Bears
